        <Parent_String>governmental functions [300075671], functions by specific context [300132458], functions (activities) [300138088], Functions (hierarchy name) [300054593], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
